name: Illamasqua Lipstick
description: Lipstick by Illamasqua - Highly pigmented lipsticks - Long-lasting, moisturising cream formula - Matte and gloss finishes

brand.name: Illamasqua
brand.description: Drawing on their rich heritage in the film and theatre industry, Illamasqua are known for creating high performance make-up with a distinctly dark side. Encouraging self expression with their vibrant berry tones and inky hues, the range consists of pigmented powder eyeshadows and eyeliners, along with rich lipsticks for a professional finish.
